        "tool": "task",
        "args": {
          "description": "Research week-4 ACL progressions",
          "prompt": "You are the researcher sub-agent for rehab-as-code. Read ONLY protocols/protocol-library/ (especially post-acl-week-4.yaml and post-acl-week-3.yaml for comparison). \n\nPatient: Andre, post-ACL reconstruction, currently on week 3 protocol with exercises: quad_sets, heel_slides, terminal_knee_extension, stationary_bike (see protocols/protocol.yaml in workspace).\n\nTask: Return candidate progressions for advancing to week 4. For each exercise from week 3, cite file:line from protocol-library for the week-4 appropriate prescription (sets, reps, load, ROM targets, durations, progression/regression criteria if in library). If week-4 library differs from week 3, list the minimal diffs. Do not edit any files. Output structured bullet list with exact protocol-library paths cited.",
