          "description": "Evaluate wearables and symptoms",
          "prompt": "You are the evaluator sub-agent. Classify symptoms and recovery risk from:\n\nWearables (2026-05-02): sleep_score 78, hrv_ms 41, recovery_score 82. Context note: HRV trend described as 32 -> 41 ms (recovered).\n\nSymptom log (protocols/data/symptoms-2026-05-02.md): mentions recovered HRV trend, sleep_score 78, asks for next week progression; no specific exercise pain reported.\n\nApply rules from protocols/.cursorrules for wearable interpretation (HRV +5ms trend = cleared to progress one exercise; -8ms = hold all; sleep <70 avg 3+ days = drop intensity 20%; recovery <60 = hold). \n\nOutput: classification (progress / hold / regress), which exercises if any may progress vs hold, risk flags, brief justification. Do not read or write protocol files beyond what you need for rules.",
